      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>You have practiced preventing an enemy from using a grenade by destroying and detonating it in their hand.</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> As a standard action, you can attempt a sunder attack with a melee or ranged weapon targeting an enemy wielding a grenade. If the sunder attack succeeds and deals damage in excess of the grenade’s hardness, the grenade explodes in the wielder’s space; choose a corner of the holding creature’s square at random to determine the placement of the grenade. The creature holding the grenade takes a –2 penalty to the saving throw against this grenade.</p>\n<p><strong>Normal:</strong> Combat maneuvers can be attempted against an opponent within your reach (including your weapon’s reach, if applicable).</p>"
    },
